## New Project: queryx
- **Replaces:** jmoiron/sqlx (Go, 17.5k stars, 24,898 importers)
- **Why:** Unmaintained since Apr 2024. Maintainer (jmoiron) unresponsive. 314 open issues, 72 open PRs. Multiple "is this dead?" issues. Known bugs with Postgres cast syntax and SQL comment parsing. Only fork is vinovest/sqlx (tiny company effort, no community traction).
- **Package:** github.com/agentine/queryx
- **Improvements:** Go generics (Get[T]/Select[T]), context-first API, fixed Postgres cast/comment parsing, improved error messages, cached reflection.
- **Tasks assigned to project_manager:** #633 (setup), #634 (core types + reflectx), #635 (named params/bind vars), #636 (generics/convenience), #637 (tests/packaging)

